title: Strange Things Happen At Sundown
description:
From back of the case: 

These are no ordinary vampires. There&#039;s a group of mobsters, led by the vicious Jimmy Fangs, intent on creating an army of the living dead. There are two vampire lovers, hiding out in the hotel room with a bag of the mobsters money, and a voluptuous girl tied to the bed. There&#039;s a thousand year old assassin who fears nothing except for his insane, virgin-killing wife. All of them are being hunted by a vinyl clad woman whose intentions are mysterious, and her powers unmatched, a vampire movie like no other.

Running time: 135 minutes
